Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 又睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好睡觉脑子会坏掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还是搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,明明收拾掉了那个妖狐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,身体还是没有复原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找 斩杀 直到复原为止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,自从离开醍醐你太逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好休息光顾着斩妖除魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去身体吃不消…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,现在威胁国家安危的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,才是鬼神！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说没了爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也要好好活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会陪着大哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,白面不动之卷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在那座山对面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢啦 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有温泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,山上会自己涌出热水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,去那里的话大哥哥也能好好休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈说温泉不仅能让身体放松
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还能让心情平静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,总之我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,传言那温泉附近有妖怪出没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓军队已退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,又降恩惠之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还不能解除和鬼神的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是我老婆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,果然这张脸也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在这过夜再合适不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找点木柴和果子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 这里说不定是强盗的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不能杀掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,教训一下就行了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,捡了很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,瀑布的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？好大的佛像…别吓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我很难吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且百鬼丸大哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是多罗罗啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别拽了好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 看看这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫阿鲣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,阿鲣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 这里是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,阿鲣一个人住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔有路人来瀑布会留下食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我就靠这些为生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚那个瀑布啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来为什么那座佛像没有脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,以前有位武士来到瀑布前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,发现了被冲刷成不动尊形状的岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,本来那位武士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为雕刻的佛像面容安详而闻名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是到了武士时代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人们开始敬仰威风满面的不动尊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,于是这位武士逐渐被人遗忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,武士想要再次得到大家的青睐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,开始在岩石上雕刻不动尊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,身体 手 脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,到最后雕刻脸的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,武士下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要雕刻出前所未有最威风的不动尊脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,雕刻出的脸全都似曾相识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雕刻完又毁掉 长年累月周而复始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,武士慢慢变老
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,最终也没能完成 抱憾而终
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这故事听不太懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对多罗罗来说还太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哇看起来真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来 请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看到这粥我想起了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来你把我叫做妈妈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我长得特别像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,简直一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么看都是我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,连声音都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟最近都没好好睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吵醒他好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这里晚上很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 第一次吃到这么好吃的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我…还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你妈妈可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,比起阿鲣 还是妈妈更合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗真是爱撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦 你喜欢就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,安心下来之后我好像也困了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 我还担心药不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚那位武士的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还有后续哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那位武士死后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不动尊不知何时被妖怪依附了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为了完成武士的遗愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,想要一张脸 想要一张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不动尊复活了武士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,命令她把活人带过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为了把人脸献给不动尊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是那位武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,通过不动尊的力量读取对方的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就能随意改变自己的相貌与声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的脸不适合不动尊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果是那个男人的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗真是爱撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那就把这张脸献给不动尊吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,把大哥哥还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我都没有捆住你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会把大哥哥交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你放开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓要跟随大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,睡得真香啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,住手吧 百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没有必要毁掉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个声音 是大哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 来妈妈身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是阿鲣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…为什么我的脸没有变？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道自己母亲的相貌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,把脸给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在寻找这张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要他的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,至今为止找到的最好的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么非要这么好的脸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有眼睛 有牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有嘴巴 这已经足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是阿鲣却肆意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,变成了一个欺骗别人 掠夺人脸的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你考虑一下被扒下脸的人的感受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,难受 不甘 伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,比所有的不动尊都好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,从何时开始 从何时开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,从何时开始 我变成了这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,放在你的脸上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对我笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个温柔的孩子 多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就像佛陀一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我本想自己先振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,却增加了你的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还让你想起了母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然大哥哥一直在帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你遇到困难的话 我绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我又搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,温泉 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,温泉附近有妖怪出现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当时…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 这里这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 我还是第一次泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看哦 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然知道你看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说 不要看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼…渗进伤口了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是所谓极乐吧 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就此死去也值了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和尚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪里出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,听你这语气真是过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在你们来之前就在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 这就是孽缘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 洗澡了 洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,洗澡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们干什么 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一直都很淘气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这附近没见过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,旅行？ 要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是要去哪个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…我还没想好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人是你的哥哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥就是大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你的背上好像写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要老盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是地图吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,地图？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,地图 是地图！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这绝对是地图
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,地图
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要老盯着人家身体看！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系吧 让我们看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了 看到了…
